{"tid":2187763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【監獄搶錢家族】霸佔訪客處賣探監用品圖利 活躍兩年月賺10萬","createTime":"2020-09-03T23:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T13:00:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"16a2e898c55314631a081a93427dddac9cb9a808","tid":2187763,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T23:51:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_757615_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_757615_0&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=4a9867a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_757615_0&h=848753dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_757615_0</a>"},{"pid":"22e7ad5dba2d779ff0715c5eb253287023936ae2","tid":2187763,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:49:22.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"facf47e9a12afd5c10a9d87cd2fd5ceacbcd6d62","tid":2187763,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:50:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Hgc4-odvzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9Hgc4-odvzU&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=4b8907d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Hgc4-odvzU</a>"},{"pid":"c10dcd9ea99fedeea5f6ba11fcae1d90facde7c5","tid":2187763,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:52:03.000Z","msg":"荔枝角收押所的訪客登記處，本是讓在囚人士的親友辦理探監手續的場所，可是，有讀者向我們報料指，每天都有一個家庭式集團在這裏販賣探監物品，更離譜的是，他們霸佔了多個原本供探監人士擺放私人物品的儲物櫃作存貨之用；不過，在場的保安人員卻一直未有阻止他們的行為。除了賣探監物品，這一家人也提供代客探監的服務，亦染指赤柱監獄的相關生意。消息指，這個監獄搶錢家族每月賺取的利潤超過十萬，相當可觀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/skipped-hk/20200904/S7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fskipped-hk%2F20200904%2FS7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI%2F&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjYaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=02d093bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fskipped-hk%2F20200904%2FS7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI%2F&h=bbe4f63c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/skipped-hk/20200904/S7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI/</a>"},{"pid":"d41bfd1389b6a14d75f487cfe3e5f4433084f969","tid":2187763,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:53:44.000Z","msg":"據悉，這個監獄搶錢家族的話事人，是一名年約50多歲叫做蓮姐的女子；荔枝角收押所為其主要地盤，她的弟弟阿強及妹妹阿珍亦不時到場拹助，幫手賣貨及代客探監，他的一對子女亦有在赤柱監獄做代探，每次收取二至三百元費用。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士透露，蓮姐之所以開始經營這盤生意，全因在兩年前一名姓陳叫Joseph的律師找蓮姐幫忙代客探監，更順道為她覓生意；蓮姐做熟之後，發覺販賣探監物品的利潤比代探更高，於是便開始展開探監和賣貨的雙線發展。"},{"pid":"ba35ebf2f42a9ddae67efc3a3d9be3c99d2f2a1c","tid":2187763,"uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:55:24.000Z","msg":"蓮姐主要售賣的貨品組合，是俗稱「五大」的五款零食，魷魚絲、沙爹肉片、薄餅、朱古力，及魚片花生，搭配16包香煙，售價$638，比收押所外的士多便宜超過兩成，因此，生意非常多。"},{"pid":"b46a39970eb57715b07366408b1e0d8c09385fa2","tid":2187763,"uid":167340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />cls"},{"pid":"437d32fdca4d5002242e0d8337aa26b572aa67d5","tid":2187763,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:58:36.000Z","msg":"咁都得<br />\n冇人報"},{"pid":"70998ca3cd36af43982fe2e1ba36fa8411020f0c","tid":2187763,"uid":82829,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:59:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51c6df1ef26d8854aa733b2b1b796abfc4171adf","tid":2187763,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"437d32fdca4d5002242e0d8337aa26b572aa67d5","tid":2187763,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T18:58:36.000Z","msg":"咁都得<br />\n冇人報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T19:00:36.00